name: MANIFESTO EAU DE PARFUM
description: To imagine fashion Saint Laurent Manifesto embodies a bold woman who created her own codes, which said yes to style, beauty and mystery. The woman Manifesto has an attitude, a laugh, a tone of voice, a presence but mostly, femininity.
ingredients: ['Jasmine (Sambac)', 'Tonka Bean', 'Blackcurrant Bud', 'Lily Of The Valley', 'Vanilla', 'Bergamot', 'Cedarwood', 'Cream (Chantilly)', 'Green Notes', 'Sandalwood']
